type: Tutorial Step - My Only Friend, The End!

definition.text: Ok, my friend, this is the end! I hope you've enjoyed the show and that I've managed to get you hooked to Superalgos!

paragraphs.text: There's no doubt in my mind that you haven't seen anything like Superalgos before, have you?
If you're one of the good souls that finish the tutorial with an unquenchable urge to get involved in the project, find the Contribute to Superalgos tutorial to the right to get on board!
That's it! I promise! Click Next if you don't believe me! Or go back one step to look into the other tutorials for more learning material!
